@startuml Signup Flows - Detailed Industry Breakdown
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam activity {
    BackgroundColor #E8F4F8
    BorderColor #2C5F7C
    FontColor #1A3A4A
}

title TWS ERP - Detailed Signup Flows by Industry

||#LightBlue|**EDUCATION FLOW (5 Steps)**|
start
:Step 1: Create Account;
note right
  Fields:
  • First Name
  • Last Name
  • Email
  • Password (12+ chars)
  • Confirm Password
  API: POST /api/signup/register
end note

:Step 2: Verify Email;
note right
  Fields:
  • 6-digit OTP
  API: POST /api/signup/verify-email
  Can resend: POST /api/signup/resend-otp
end note

:Step 3: School Information;
note right
  Fields:
  • School Name
  • School Type (K-12/College/University)
  • School Email (optional)
  • School Phone (optional)
end note

:Step 4: Set Up Tenant;
note right
  Fields:
  • Tenant Subdomain (slug)
  API: GET /api/signup/check-slug-availability
  Real-time validation
end note

:Step 5: Welcome Confirmation;
note right
  API: POST /api/signup/create-tenant
  Redirect: https://[slug].tws.example.com/onboarding
end note
stop

